query:
INSERT INTO registrations (
            id,
            client_id,
            machine_id,
            common_access_card_id,
            registration_request_id,
            election_id,
            precinct_id,
            ballot_style_id
        )
        VALUES (
            $1, $2, $3, $4,
            (SELECT id FROM registration_requests WHERE client_id = $5),
            (SELECT id FROM elections WHERE client_id = $6),
            $7, $8
        )
